      <title>莱坊：迪拜房价将在 2025 年再次飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/dubai-home-prices-set-to-surge-again-in-2025-knight-frank-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莱坊表示，迪拜房价在 2024 年已上涨 20%，明年可能还会进一步上涨，这标志着疫情后开始的强劲复苏势头的延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/dubai-home-prices-set-to-surge-again-in-2025-knight-frank-says</guid>
